name: NOISE - oshi - i know you're tired of driving

attributes.trait_type: oshi - i know you're tired of driving

metadata.description:
Artist, producer, and DJ oshi delivers the perfect sad boy summer bop with “i know you’re tired of driving.” Angsty, raw and broodingly romantic, Oshi wears his heart on his sleeve. “i know you’re tired of driving” captures unfiltered emotion while managing to result in a compelling final product, ready for club tears all summer long. 

Inspired by a drum sample, oshi utilizes a chopped vocal and glitchy drum break to add a satisfying element of danceability, “Sometimes I make songs just to work through feelings.”  

----

This is the twelfth track from HIGH FREQUENCY Volume 1—a compilation album curated by NOISE.

Read interviews with each artist at noisedao.mirror.xyz.
